			<div class="content" id="post-content-1933090">
									

<p>EDIT: And I AM DONE!</p>
<p>The GOC Canon is now open for editing.</p>
<p>The hub page is divided into three sections. The first contains all the background information about the Coalition, and all of the cool stuff like threat entity files and handbooks that make up the world background.</p>
<p>The second page is made up of personnel profiles. Whether they're author avatars or characters in your stories, put your information here. At the moment, it's a bit spartan, but it'll get fleshed out soon.</p>
<p>The third page is for tales. If your tale is part of a series, create a tab for it. Otherwise, put it under Misc. Tales.</p>

							</div>

								
